---
import { FadeIn } from '../ui/FadeIn';
import { CheckCircle2, XCircle } from 'lucide-react';
---

<section id="ciblage" class="py-24 md:py-32 bg-bg relative">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-5xl">
    <FadeIn client:visible>
      <div class="text-center mb-20">
        <h2 class="text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-accent mb-4">Profil de pilotage</h2>
        <p class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white italic uppercase tracking-tighter">
          Est-ce que cette formation est <br /> <span class="text-accent">votre prochain virage ?</span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </FadeIn>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 md:gap-12">
      {/* OUI Column */}
      <FadeIn client:visible delay={0.1}>
        <div class="bg-surface p-10 rounded-[24px] border border-accent/20 h-full relative overflow-hidden group">
          <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-accent/5 blur-3xl rounded-full translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2"></div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8 relative z-10">
            <CheckCircle2 class="w-8 h-8 text-accent" />
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-white italic uppercase">C'est OUI si...</h3>
          </div>
          <ul class="space-y-6 text-text-secondary relative z-10">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-accent mt-2.5 flex-shrink-0"></div>
              <p>Vous voulez un <span class="text-white italic">avis impartial</span> basé sur le réel.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-accent mt-2.5 flex-shrink-0"></div>
              <p>Vous voulez <span class="text-white italic">organiser votre logistique</span> sans stress.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-accent mt-2.5 flex-shrink-0"></div>
              <p>Vous voulez transformer l'absence d'embrayage en <span class="text-white italic">plaisir de pilotage.</span></p>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </FadeIn>

      {/* NON Column */}
      <FadeIn client:visible delay={0.2}>
        <div class="bg-surface p-10 rounded-[24px] border border-white/5 h-full relative group hover:border-white/10 transition-colors">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8">
            <XCircle class="w-8 h-8 text-text-secondary/50" />
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-text-secondary italic uppercase">C'est NON si...</h3>
          </div>
          <ul class="space-y-6 text-text-secondary/60">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-white/20 mt-2.5 flex-shrink-0"></div>
              <p>Vous cherchez un simple <span class="italic text-white/40">guide d'achat</span> de prix.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-white/20 mt-2.5 flex-shrink-0"></div>
              <p>Vous voulez un cours d'ingénierie pure sur les moteurs.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-white/20 mt-2.5 flex-shrink-0"></div>
              <p>Vous pensez que seule l'odeur de l'essence fait un motard.</p>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </FadeIn>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
